If it be ſaid that he who ſweareth by the creatures amiſſe forſweareth himſelfe; 
                              Obj. 
                            then hee who ſweareth the truth by the creatures, hee ſweareth by God: hee diſhonoureth God when hee ſweareth by the creatures falſely, therefore hee honoureth God when hee ſweareth by the creatures truely.

